ORAGNIZER: Eileen
CONTACT: http://photo.meetup.c...
WHO: All members.

I guess Trident Booksellers & Cafe is really busy and not much room so let's meet at Starbucks on Boylston between Exeter & Fairfield. It's spacious and normally you can catch a parking spot on Boylston at this time of day.

Starbucks
755 Boylston Street
Boston MA, 02116
United States
6:30pm

This will be a night shoot around Boston. We need 10 people to hold this event.

BRING A TRIPOD and dress warm as we'll head out and capture Boston at night!

Cheers, Eileen
